  "texts": [
    "I aim to remedy this putative weakness here.",
    "By saying that AI is 'capable' of disempowering humanity I mean the following: if the AI would try to disempower humanity, it would succeed.",
    "This is a non-technical notion familiar from ordinary discourse.",
    "For instance, we may say that Magnus Carlsen is capable of beating me at chess.",
    "He wouldn't necessarily win against me, for he could lose intentionally."
  ],
